<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="B客戶">
  <data key="d0">B客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">customer</data>
  <data key="d2">B客戶 is a term used to denote the customer for whom maintenance activities and records are documented. This entity plays a crucial role in maintaining transparency and accountability within maintenance operations. By clearly associating each maintenance activity or record with the appropriate B客戶, it ensures that all relevant information about the maintenance performed is accurately attributed to the correct customer.

B客戶 is integral to documenting maintenance records, making sure that every piece of data related to maintenance activities is properly linked to the specific customer. This association helps in maintaining a clear and organized system where each B客戶 can easily track their maintenance history and ensure that all necessary actions are taken for their equipment or services.

The term B客戶 is consistently used across various contexts to refer to the customer involved in maintenance documentation, emphasizing its importance in the overall maintenance process. Whether it involves recording activities or documenting records, B客戶 remains a key entity that ensures the integrity and accuracy of maintenance information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518</data>
