<node id="Indexer">
  <data key="d0">Indexer</data>
  <data key="d1">indexer</data>
  <data key="d2">The Indexer is a component added to the IDX cluster node for B部門.&lt;SEP&gt;Indexer is a component that was added to the IDX cluster and is being monitored for index synchronization status.&lt;SEP&gt;Indexer is a system component that UF devices are supposed to connect to but have failed to do so.&lt;SEP&gt;Indexer is a component added to the IDX cluster, with its synchronization status being monitored.&lt;SEP&gt;Indexer is a component that UF devices failed to connect with, leading to maintenance actions.&lt;SEP&gt;The Indexer's synchronization status was confirmed to be normal during the maintenance activities.&lt;SEP&gt;Indexer is a system component that UF units failed to connect with, leading to maintenance actions.</data>
