<node id="Splunk">
  <data key="d0">Splunk</data>
  <data key="d1">service</data>
  <data key="d2">Splunk is a monitoring service used for overseeing host systems during maintenance processes. It requires regular upkeep, including weekly onsite maintenance activities. These tasks encompass various actions such as IP adjustments, package upgrades, version upgrades, certificate renewal, path modification, performance checks, and user permission adjustments. Additionally, Splunk necessitates the disabling of automatic version checks.

The service has roles with specific capabilities, indicating a structured approach to its management. It is utilized by E客戶 (E customers), who require regular maintenance and updates to ensure optimal performance. The need for onsite maintenance highlights the importance of physical presence in managing Splunk's operations effectively. Issues related to bundle storage and indexer synchronization are also part of the maintenance process.

Splunk is also used as a monitoring system to handle logs, which initially failed to capture all pice_logs files due to their similarity. This indicates that Splunk's logging capabilities require careful configuration to ensure comprehensive data capture.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk is a service that was upgraded from version 9.3.3 to 9.3.8 during the maintenance.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk is a service that requires onsite maintenance and has roles with abnormal capabilities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f0773b8daffa7a65254a73867e36afb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518</data>
