<node id="Maintenance Record">
  <data key="d0">Maintenance Record</data>
  <data key="d1">record</data>
  <data key="d2">The Maintenance Record is a comprehensive document that details various aspects of maintenance activities and processes. It serves multiple purposes across different clients and scenarios.

For A客戶, the Maintenance Record documents specific activities related to their system during designated maintenance periods. This includes detailed information about maintenance tasks performed on their Splunk service, as well as actions taken to address issues with Splunk SH for C客戶. Additionally, it records the handling of a missing file issue for D客戶 by B人員.

For B客戶, the Maintenance Record focuses on documenting the activities and actions taken during the maintenance process. This includes specific details about maintenance tasks performed on 2025/11/19 from 13:30 to 14:30, as well as broader actions taken to address various issues.

The record also provides detailed information about maintenance activities performed on specific dates and times, such as the upgrade of Splunk for A客戶. For instance, it documents the details of maintenance tasks performed on 2025/12/19 from 13:30 to 18:00.

Overall, the Maintenance Record is a critical tool for tracking and managing maintenance activities, ensuring that all necessary actions are documented and issues are addressed promptly.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record details the activities performed by C人員for B客戶, including the time frame and actions taken.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record documents the activities and actions taken for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record documents the details of the maintenance task performed on B客戶's servers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7743e93210e95e8e40e0d2a627684b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-345e520afd2a192e25824abb33740d46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f0773b8daffa7a65254a73867e36afb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b</data>
