<node id="DEP02">
  <data key="d0">DEP02</data>
  <data key="d1">server</data>
  <data key="d2">DEP02 is a server that is currently undergoing several maintenance and migration tasks. The server, identified by its IP address [IP], is scheduled for transfer next week as part of the ongoing maintenance activities. This transfer requires root service confirmation to ensure a smooth transition. DEP02 is associated with A部門 (Department A) and will need connectivity checks post-transfer.

The maintenance tasks involve specific actions related to remote configuration file backup scripts, which are crucial for ensuring data integrity during the migration process. Additionally, after the server was transferred previously, its services were verified to confirm correct operation. This verification step is essential to ensure that all functionalities of DEP02 remain intact and operational following the transfer.

Overall, the migration of DEP02 involves careful planning and execution to minimize downtime and maintain service continuity for A部門 (Department A).</data>
