<edge source="B客戶" target="A人員">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between A人員 and B客戶 is centered around various aspects of system maintenance and support. A人員 plays a crucial role in handling maintenance tasks for B客戶, which includes resolving issues that arise within B客戶's systems. This involves not only the physical upkeep but also the documentation and record-keeping of these maintenance activities. The responsibilities of A人員 extend to ensuring that all maintenance records are accurately handled, providing a comprehensive overview of the system's health and performance over time.

A人員 is deeply involved in the maintenance activities for B客戶, ensuring that systems run smoothly and any issues are promptly addressed. This role encompasses handling maintenance tasks, maintaining accurate records, and being assigned to oversee these critical functions. A人員 is specifically identified as an engineer responsible for managing the maintenance record of B客戶, highlighting the technical expertise required for this position. The consistent involvement of A人員 in these activities underscores their essential contribution to the upkeep and performance of B客戶's systems.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is involved in handling maintenance tasks for B客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">customer support,engineering,engineering support,handling,maintenance,task assignment,task handling</data>
