C人員 is assigned to handle these maintenance tasks, which are crucial for ensuring the smooth operation and upkeep of B客戶's systems. Their involvement makes them an integral part of the support framework for B客戶. This includes handling the maintenance record of B客戶, managing maintenance activities, and addressing specific maintenance issues that may arise.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is involved in handling maintenance tasks for B客戶.</data>
