<edge source="C人員" target="E客戶">
  <data key="d7">19.0</data>
  <data key="d8">C人員 is an engineer who plays a crucial role in managing and maintaining various aspects of E客戶's systems. C人員 is primarily responsible for handling the maintenance records of E客戶, ensuring that all maintenance tasks are documented accurately and efficiently. This responsibility highlights C人員's role as the designated engineer for this task, emphasizing their active involvement in meeting E客戶's maintenance needs.

In addition to managing maintenance records, C人員 is specifically tasked with maintaining E客戶's Splunk instance. This involves handling the maintenance of E客戶's Splunk system, which is a critical component of their operations. C人員's responsibilities include conducting various maintenance activities and tasks related to E客戶, ensuring that the systems remain operational and efficient.

C人員's role encompasses a broad range of engineering responsibilities, all aimed at ensuring that E客戶's maintenance needs are met effectively. This includes handling maintenance records, maintaining Splunk instances, and performing other necessary maintenance tasks as part of their overall duties.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is the engineer responsible for handling maintenance tasks for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is the engineer responsible for handling maintenance tasks for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is responsible for handling maintenance tasks for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is handling the maintenance record for E客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">customer support,engineering support,handling,maintenance,task handling</data>
